scene.message:
Yukino: Aw man, here too...{nl}
...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...wait, what!{waitkey}{clearbox}It's the teachers! Asleep.{nl}
Get it together, sheesh.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hm. The situation{nl}
seems graver than I imagined.{nl}
There must surely be some{waitkey}{clearbox}"thing" putting the people{nl}
of the school to sleep.{nl}
We must find it first.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Argh! Pathetic!{nl}
Here I am, a mere student,{nl}
working this hard,{waitkey}{clearbox}and the teachers slacking{nl}
off like this - what gives?!{nl}
Get it together, really.{waitkey}{ret}

V.P. Hannya: Zzz... zzz...{wait_fr:30}guh!{nl}
gaah...{wait_fr:30}grind grind...{wait_fr:30}grr...{nl}
heh heh...{wait_fr:30}guhuhuhu...{wait_fr:30}heh...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ew~ this baldy's{nl}
fast asleep with a creepy{nl}
grin - so gross!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hideous... I can't{nl}
bear to look. That such a man{nl}
calls himself an educator -{nl}
the world's gone to ruin.{waitkey}{clearbox}But is the Principal okay?{nl}
He's groaning quite badly.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh my! The Principal{nl}
is groaning. Such a{nl}
terrible sweat.{waitkey}{clearbox}Is this also the Snow{nl}
Queen's magic at work?{waitkey}{ret}

Principal Oishi: Zzz... zzz...{nl}
nn{wait_fr:30}nngh...{nl}
...but{wait_fr:30}... that is...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Same as the room{nl}
before.{waitkey}{clearbox}Neither of them will wake{nl}
no matter what we try.{nl}
What do we do?{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: You're not planning{nl}
to just leave the sleeping{nl}
folk like this, are you?{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: It's a chance, so~{nl}
shall we doodle on{nl}
Hannya's bald head?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly...! Why did{nl}
we enter the tower? To escape{nl}
the school, was it not?{waitkey}{clearbox}Then think of nothing else{nl}
and press on! There's much{nl}
waste in your actions.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hmm{wait_fr:30}...hm{wait_fr:30}...hm{wait_fr:30}...hm{nl}
...!{wait_fr:30} Right! As your leader,{nl}
I, the great me, command:{waitkey}{clearbox}press on!{wait_fr:30}...but...{wait_fr:30} hold on.{nl}
Saving these guys to earn{nl}
a favor sounds good too. Hmm?{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Standing here like this{nl}
only wastes time...{nl}
Whether we wake the sleepers{waitkey}{clearbox}or clear the tower, what{nl}
matters most for us now{nl}
is to move forward.{waitkey}{ret}
